most of these people aren't even qualified

12
00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:15.659
to be up here in the first place.

13
00:01:16.409 --> 00:01:20.287
But now you're all what?
Down with the common man?

14
00:01:20.289 --> 00:01:22.789
Don't try to make this about me. Dani.

15
00:01:22.790 --> 00:01:26.835
You know as well as I do that Helios.
NASA. Roscosmos

16
00:01:26.837 --> 00:01:28.212
and all the other M-7 countries.

17
00:01:28.212 --> 00:01:30.673
they don't give two shits
about these workers.

18
00:01:30.674 --> 00:01:33.968
Commander Poole.
we are the ones who transformed this base

19
00:01:33.968 --> 00:01:36.762
from a couple of habs
into a viable mining colony.

20
00:01:36.763 --> 00:01:39.640
And all we are asking
is for you to honor the deal.

21
00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:43.477
If we let that rock go to Earth's orbit.
most of our jobs are gone within a year.

22
00:01:44.563 --> 00:01:48.399
What if Helios offered you some kind of...
...guaranteed retraining?

23
00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:49.859
Right?

24
00:01:49.859 --> 00:01:52.235
More education. an opportunity for you...

25
00:01:52.236 --> 00:01:53.820
Forgive us. Forgive us.

26
00:01:53.822 --> 00:01:56.115
We've heard that one before.
It's never anything but bullshit.

27
00:01:56.115 --> 00:01:58.950
Listen. if you want your cryo center
to start making the fuel

28
00:01:58.951 --> 00:02:00.368
you need to launch for Goldilocks.

29
00:02:00.370 --> 00:02:02.579
if you want your cargo to get unloaded
from <i>Phoenix</i>.

30
00:02:02.581 --> 00:02:05.707
if you want your habitation units to be
constructed or your food prepared. we...

31
00:02:05.709 --> 00:02:10.463
I have gone out of my way
