Our power is in sticking together.

70
00:05:27.244 --> 00:05:29.411
They start peeling us off.
this whole thing crumbles.

71
00:05:29.413 --> 00:05:31.329
Look. I came up here to earn.

72
00:05:31.331 --> 00:05:34.125
And all I know is right now.
I'm not earning nothing.

73
00:05:34.125 --> 00:05:36.918
Yeah. well. neither are they.
And they're starting to panic.

74
00:05:38.004 --> 00:05:40.630
- We have to hold the course here.
- Right. You gotta be strong.

75
00:05:40.632 --> 00:05:43.425
You heard what Palmer said.
They're gonna shitcan all of us.

76
00:05:43.427 --> 00:05:45.095
They can't. There's no time.

77
00:05:46.305 --> 00:05:50.432
Listen up. I just heard they're gonna try
