85
00:06:45.112 --> 00:06:46.906
It's a clever move.
You gotta give it to 'em.

86
00:06:49.451 --> 00:06:51.744
We gotta get creative. Right?

87
00:06:51.745 --> 00:06:53.370
How are we gonna solve this?

88
00:06:53.372 --> 00:06:55.747
We have to get back over
to that cryo center

89
00:06:55.749 --> 00:06:58.959
or we're not gonna have enough fuel
when it comes time to get Goldilocks.

90
00:06:58.961 --> 00:07:02.547
It's just too far a distance
for any sort of improvised pressure suit.

91
00:07:02.548 --> 00:07:05.257
And it's gonna take too long
to make a new one from scratch.

92
00:07:05.259 --> 00:07:06.341
Just stop.

93
00:07:06.343 --> 00:07:08.636
Here we are on the cusp
of grabbing something

94
00:07:08.637 --> 00:07:10.680
